node.text:
It’s quite telling when even #CNN turns on #JoeBiden and calls him a foreign policy failure. All you had to do was look at his past. In the Obama admin, every general said that Joe has been on the wrong side of every single foreign policy decision for the last few DECADES. They were all right, and now we have even more proof. 

 #JakeTapper: We are “watching a tragic foreign policy disaster unfold before our eyes...The rapid crumbling of #Afghanistan has caught the #Biden #WhiteHouse flat footed.”

“It seems shocking that President Biden could’ve been so wrong” 

#SleepyJoe #KamalaHarris #Comeonman

node.title: Jake Tapper: We‘re “Watching a Tragic Foreign Policy Disaster Unfold …”

node.text: #Florida Governor (and future President) #RonDeSantis completely takes apart #JoeBiden on his failed handling of the border and his failure to lead on a myriad of issues.  This comes after the Biden administration told #DeSantis to “get out of the way” on Covid. How do Democrats not see that having an open border, especially right now, is a really bad idea?  Aren’t they trying to lower infections?  Just a guess but having an open border probably isn’t going to help with that…

node.title: FL Gov. Ron DeSantis Destroys Joe Biden on Covid & Southern Border

“Are you saying that #OAN is not a credible news source?”

… Saying OAN is not credible is pretty funny coming from CNN …

node.text:
Afghan reporter #NaziraKarimi gets very emotional during #Pentagon briefing:

"I'm very upset today because Afghan women didn't expect overnight that all the #Taliban came. They took off my flag-this is my flag-they put their flag. Everybody is upset...Where is my president?!" Wow. You can feel the utter frustration in her voice. Could #JoeBiden really not do any better?  I think most people were in agreement that we should leave #Afghanistan but there is a good, bad and terrible way to do that and it’s unfortunate #SleepyJoe chose the latter.

node.text: Here’s what we heard from the #Biden admin over the last couple weeks and days about #Afghanistan. Listen as #JoeBiden,  his #presssecretary #JenPsaki and his #Pentagon spokesman #JohnKirby all down-play the situation.  Quite the trifecta of incompetence. Way to go, Joe! But fear not America, because #SleepyJoe will be cutting his vacation short today, coming back to the #WhiteHouse and addressing the nation at 12:45 PST / 3:45 EST. #comeonman

At least 63 people on #MarthasVineyard have tested positive for Covid since #BarackObama's maskless 60th birthday bash - the most cases on the island since April. 'At this time we're not aware of any cases connected to the Obama party,' Tisbury health agent and boards of health spokesperson Maura Valley told @dailymail . 'It's a little too early and the only way we're going to know is through comprehensive contact tracing.'

Hundreds of people attended Obama's birthday bash Saturday, flying in from around the country and congregating under tents where partiers danced, ate and drank the night away on his estate in Edgartown.
